  "raw_html": "<main class=\"bd-main\" id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\">\n<div class=\"bd-content\">\n<div class=\"bd-article-container\">\n<div class=\"bd-header-article d-print-none\">\n<div class=\"header-article-items header-article__inner\">\n<div class=\"header-article-items__start\">\n<div class=\"header-article-item\">\n<nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"d-print-none\">\n<ul class=\"bd-breadcrumbs\">\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item breadcrumb-home\">\n<a aria-label=\"Home\" class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../index.html\">\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-home\"></i>\n</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../pytorch-api.html\">Reference API</a></li>\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../torch.html\">torch</a></li>\n<li aria-current=\"page\" class=\"breadcrumb-item active\">torch.take</li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"header-article-items__end\">\n<div class=\"header-article-item\">\n<div class=\"rating\">\n    Rate this Page\n    <div class=\"stars\">\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"1\" data-value=\"1\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"2\" data-value=\"2\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"3\" data-value=\"3\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"4\" data-value=\"4\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"5\" data-value=\"5\">★</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"searchbox\"></div>\n<article class=\"bd-article\" id=\"pytorch-article\">\n<!-- Hidden breadcrumb schema for SEO only -->\n<div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<link href=\"../pytorch-api.html\" itemprop=\"item\"/>\n<meta content=\"Reference API\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"1\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<link href=\"../torch.html\" itemprop=\"item\"/>\n<meta content=\"torch\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"2\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<meta content=\"torch.take\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"3\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"searchbox\"></div>\n<article class=\"bd-article\">\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"torch-take\">\n<h1>torch.take<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#torch-take\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">#</a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"torch.take\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">torch.</span></span><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">take</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">input</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">index</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span> <span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../tensors.html#torch.Tensor\" title=\"torch.Tensor\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></a></span></span><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#torch.take\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">#</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Returns a new tensor with the elements of <code class=\"xref py py-attr docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">input</span></code> at the given indices.\nThe input tensor is treated as if it were viewed as a 1-D tensor. The result\ntakes the same shape as the indices.</p>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">Parameters</dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\"><ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><strong>input</strong> (<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../tensors.html#torch.Tensor\" title=\"torch.Tensor\"><em>Tensor</em></a>) – the input tensor.</p></li>\n<li><p><strong>index</strong> (<em>LongTensor</em>) – the indices into tensor</p></li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">src</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">torch</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tensor</span><span class=\"p\">([[</span><span class=\"mi\">4</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">... </span>                    <span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"p\">]])</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">torch</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">take</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">torch</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tensor</span><span class=\"p\">([</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"p\">]))</span>\n<span class=\"go\">tensor([ 4,  5,  8])</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</dd></dl>\n</div>\n</article>\n</article>\n<footer class=\"bd-footer-article\">\n<div class=\"footer-article-items footer-article__inner\">\n<div class=\"footer-article-item\">\n<div class=\"feedback\">\n<div class=\"rating\">\n    Rate this Page\n    <div class=\"stars\">\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"1\" data-value=\"1\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"2\" data-value=\"2\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star